{"tid":1680823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【毒氣傷屯門兒童  警察話唔關事就算？】","createTime":"2019-10-29T04:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T09:02:04.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5c34c83aab7539315da7e291f22240052b8e2863","tid":1680823,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"【毒氣傷屯門兒童  警察話唔關事就算？】<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午屯門被不明毒氣侵襲。有屯門街坊的三歲小朋友4點45分離開青雲路的幼稚園，步行十分鐘回家後發現頸和膊頭出滿紅疹（如圖），痕癢非常。<br />\n<br />\n街坊表示，小朋友在離開學校時已戴上口罩，她自己回家後也覺得喉嚨不舒服。<br />\n<br />\n一夜過後，紅疹已大致退了。由於小朋友從來沒有濕疹等皮膚問題，街坊相信與昨午侵襲屯門的刺激性氣體有關。<br />\n<br />\n現呼籲昨日出現同樣症狀的街坊與我們聯絡。另，聲稱毒氣與自己無關的香港警察，請查明毒氣來源，盡快公布；不要以催淚毒氣解決要求交代的屯門人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUwvwUC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUwvwUC.jpg&h=cedafefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/201155333283732/posts/2535959936469915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F201155333283732%2Fposts%2F2535959936469915%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=e0e08ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/201155333283732/posts/2535959936469915/</a>"},{"pid":"7b80379a3040acec52067e737dd635ed7b5efbca","tid":1680823,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"$1交稅攬炒機械人小測成績表已出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679773</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9334f06ae51c1dc093b2175a84ee1abbd3b0583f","tid":1680823,"uid":282744,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSKpBm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSKpBm1.jpg&h=4ee591cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"428c662c5cb53451f29fd5f21ed147e1034a2576","tid":1680823,"uid":80970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"